1.0.name: wordpress/fishytweet
1.0.description: Adds a link to each post that points the user to Twitter.com. Before the redirect, the URL for the actual post is sent to Tinyurl.com and the tinyurl-ified URL is used as an argument to Twitter.com thus putting it in the status field when the page loads.
